.TH "CITADEL" "1" "Jul 2026" "AceTeam" "Citadel CLI Manual"

.SH NAME
citadel - Citadel is the agent for the AceTeam Sovereign Compute Fabric


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBcitadel [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Connect your hardware to AceTeam with a single command.

.PP
Just run 'citadel' — it handles login, network connection, and launches the
control center. All other subcommands are for scripting and advanced use.


.SH OPTIONS
\fB--daemon\fP[=false]
	Run in background daemon mode (no TUI)

.PP
\fB--debug\fP[=false]
	Enable debug output

.PP
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for citadel

.PP
\fB--no-auto-update\fP[=false]
	Disable automatic update checks and installs for this run (or set CITADEL_NO_AUTO_UPDATE=1)

.PP
\fB--no-color\fP[=false]
	Disable colorized output

.PP
\fB--no-mouse\fP[=false]
	Disable control-center mouse control (keeps terminal drag-to-copy)


